Generic_FileStore

Used for representing a single continuous date period using two LocalDate instances - Generic_LocalDateRange.start and Generic_LocalDateRange.end.
Generic_Math
Generic Math Methods for adding two Numbers and testing if Numbers are in the range of other Numbers.
Generic_Memory
An interface for handling issues related to computer memory.
Generic_MemoryManager
A class to be extended for memory management involving the controlled swapping of parts of data from the fast access memory to files and the handling of OutOfMemoryErrors should they be encountered.
Generic_MemoryTest
For getting information about computer memory.
Generic_Object
To be generally extended by other classes in this library.
Generic_Path
Serializable class for a Path.
Generic_String
